<plot>A young mother with a baby is on a train going back to their Homecountry. The baby has died of unknown causes. Young mother is devastated. She wants the dead baby to be buried in their Homecountry. The Border control poses many problems for her in her journey. Passengers around her are also causing problems. The young mother has to pretend that the baby is alive. In one moving scene the mother has to sing to her dead baby to fool the border officers as well as the nosy passengers.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?425188</url></doc>
